section.step.padded(data-step="intro" data-flow="column")
  .content
    :marked
      JavaScript can bring a site to life.
      Web developers can take advantage of high quality features as quickly as they can paste an embed code.

      Many WordPress users may find that pasting a `<script>` tag to install a tool onto their site is simply too technical.
      WordPress plugins allow these non-technical users to use more tools with a few clicks.

      Creating a plugin by hand can be time consuming.
      IWP wraps your embed code and creates a plugin that is ready for the WordPress Plugin Directory.

